    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just looking at the numbers again and it's so frustrating. it's like every time i think i'm making progress, the interest just pulls it all back. is there anything in the fine print or the standard way these loans are set up that acts like a trap? like, is there a way to combat that momentum so the debt doesn't just keep eating my payments?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
